str2: But, except, however. Neuter plural of allos; properly, other things, i.e. contrariwise.

str2: (a) I empty, (b) I deprive of content, make unreal. From kenos; to make empty, i.e. to abase, neutralize, falsify.

Form, shape, outward appearance. Perhaps from the base of meros; shape; figuratively, nature.

str2: A prolongation and middle voice form of a primary verb; to cause to be, i.e. to become, used with great latitude.
In, on, among. A primary preposition denoting position, and instrumentality, i.e. A relation of rest; 'in, ' at, on, by, etc.
From homoioo; a form; abstractly, resemblance.
